text: Leung Chun-ying, GBM, GBS, JP (; born 12 August 1954), also known as CY Leung, is a Hong Kong politician. He was the third Chief Executive of Hong Kong between 2012 and 2017. ==References== Category:1954 births Category:Living people Category:Chinese businesspeople Category:Chief Executives of Hong Kong
